  "texts": [
    "As we will show in this paper, ML techniques often fill this gap.",
    "The smart building ecosystem is illustrated in Figure 1.",
    "Occupants constitute the basic building block of the ecosystem.",
    "Being the consumers of the facilities that a building provides, occupants necessitate the regulation of the building systems to achieve the desired environment.",
    "The building comprises structures, devices, and systems in place to control and maintain the desired environment for the occupants, along with diagnostic systems to ensure robust operation."
